ZH: 我们去南方度假。
EN: We are going on vacation to the south.

ZH: 南风吹拂着我的脸。
EN: The south wind is blowing gently on my face.

ZH: 上海位于中国的东南部。
EN: Shanghai is located in the southeast of China.

ZH: 这条街的南边有一家小餐馆。
EN: There is a small restaurant on the south side of this street.

ZH: 南极洲是世界上最南端的大陆。
EN: Antarctica is the southernmost continent in the world.

ZH: 夏天南方的天气很炎热。
EN: The weather in the south is very hot during summer.

ZH: 我们一路向南驾驶。
EN: We are driving south all the way.

ZH: 他们正在南部的湖边钓鱼。
EN: They are fishing by the lake in the south.

ZH: 我的家乡在中国的西南部。
EN: My hometown is in the southwest of China.

ZH: 南美洲有很多热带雨林。
EN: South America has many tropical rainforests.

ZH: 我希望能在南部的海滩上度假。
EN: I hope to vacation on the beaches in the south.

ZH: 南北极的气温非常低。
EN: The temperatures at the North and South Poles are very low.

ZH: 南方的人们习惯吃辣。
EN: People in the south are used to eating spicy food.

ZH: 这个城市的南边有一座大桥。
EN: There is a big bridge on the south side of this city.

ZH: 南非是个多元文化的国家。
EN: South Africa is a multicultural country.

ZH: 我们乘飞机往南飞。
EN: We are flying south by plane.

ZH: 南部的艺术品多具有当地特色。
EN: The artworks in the south often have local characteristics.

ZH: 探险家们在南极冒险。
EN: The explorers are embarking on an adventure in Antarctica.

ZH: 起风了，南方降雨了。
EN: The wind is blowing, it is raining in the south.

ZH: 他们正往南方前进，迎接新的挑战。
EN: They are heading south to face new challenges.
